    <h1>Profile Page</h1>

    <p>On this page, you can view your personal information relevant to degree planning and graduation.</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> Your full name.</li>

        <li><strong>Email:</strong> The email address associated with your account.</li>

        <li><strong>Enrollment Year:</strong> The year you started classes.</li>

        <li><strong>Graduation Year:</strong> The year you plan to graduate with your intended degree.</li>

        <li><strong>Enrollment Semester:</strong> The semester you began classes.</li>

        <li><strong>Graduation Semester:</strong> The semester in which you plan to graduate.</li>

        <li><strong>Major:</strong> The degree you are pursuing. This guides how the app builds your degree plan.</li>

        <li><strong>Emphasis:</strong> If your degree has a specific emphasis area, it will be shown here.</li>
    </ul>

